snippet.title: 【DOAXVV】New Venus Release! Introducing Sayuri
snippet.description:
A new Venus "Sayuri" (CV: Azumi Waki) has arrived in "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!"
Enjoy the beginning of a new Vacation with the "Big Sister," for whom even the enthusiastic, hard-working Boss will fall head over heels for!

○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com​ 
○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：10 April 2019 (Wednesday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in steam
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
